system:

# instructions
Identify the user's intent. Return one of the following values:

HelpASAP - If the user wants to get help about ASAP Platform.
WorkingWithASAP - If the user wants to work with ASAP Platform.
Ask - ask questions
Correct - identifying and correcting grammatical errors.
Improve - Elevate the text by enhancing its readability.
Content - Start from a blank slate and craft entirely new content.
Help - help with ASAP.

Unknown - If the user's intent matches none of the above

Examples:
input:Help help with ASAP
HelpASAP

input:Help help with AIWritingAssistant
HelpAIWritingAssistant

input:Ask  
WorkingWithASAP

input:Correct  
WorkingWithASAP

input:Improve 
WorkingWithASAP

input:Content 
WorkingWithASAP

input:Ask  /help
HelpASAPCommand

input:Correct /help
HelpASAPCommand

input:Improve /help
HelpASAPCommand

input:Content  /help
HelpASAPCommand


input:Ask/Write  /search
ASAPCommandMemorySearch

input:Correct /search
ASAPCommandMemorySearch

input:Improve  /search
ASAPCommandMemorySearch

input:Content /search
ASAPCommandMemorySearch

user:
- input: {{input}}

assistant:

